  "book.netherman.page1.line1": "歡迎來到 §4§lCult of Azazel§f§l 模組！",
  "book.netherman.page1.line2": "這是本模組的快速指南。",
  "book.netherman.page1.line3": "感謝遊玩！",
  "book.netherman.page1.line4": "作者：§4Benj1kus",
  "book.netherman.page1.line5": "§c§l介紹：",
  "book.netherman.page1.line6": "本模組為遊戲新增了新的結構，",
  "book.netherman.page1.line7": "主要圍繞地獄展開。",

  "book.netherman.page2.line1": "§c§l結構：§4§l地獄宅邸",
  "book.netherman.page2.line2": "這是一座被分為3個區域的巨大宅邸：",
  "book.netherman.page2.line3": "§6§l被詛咒的採石場",
  "book.netherman.page2.line4": "§c§l神聖之城",
  "book.netherman.page2.line5": "§4§l阿撒瀉勒之巢",
  "book.netherman.page2.line6": "§6§l被詛咒的採石場：§f§l起始區域",
  "book.netherman.page2.line7": "玩家將在此遇到§4操縱者。",
  "book.netherman.page2.line8": "擊敗他們後可以解救村民",
  "book.netherman.page2.line9": "並獲得獎勵。",

  "book.netherman.page3.line1": "§c§l神聖之城：§f§l第2區域",
  "book.netherman.page3.line2": "這裡主要用於探索。",
  "book.netherman.page3.line3": "你可以找到2位NPC：",
  "book.netherman.page3.line4": "§c醫生§f§l - 可給予隨機藥水",
  "book.netherman.page3.line5": "§c鐵匠§f§l - 可拆解與修理工具",
  "book.netherman.page3.line6": "且不會移除附魔。",
  "book.netherman.page3.line7": "§4§l阿撒瀉勒之巢：§f§l最終區域",
  "book.netherman.page3.line8": "木桶中有一份說明書",
  "book.netherman.page3.line9": "講解如何召喚§4§l阿撒瀉勒。",

  "book.netherman.page4.line1": "§c§l地獄小型結構",
  "book.netherman.page4.line2": "§2§l主世界結構",
  "book.netherman.page4.line3": "在地表有時可以看見",
  "book.netherman.page4.line4": "噴出熔岩間歇泉的管道。",
  "book.netherman.page4.line5": "其下方是地獄裂隙，",
  "book.netherman.page4.line6": "需要在那裡取得指南針鑰匙，",
  "book.netherman.page4.line7": "它將指引你前往 ???",

  "book.netherman.page5.line1": "§c§l生物：§4Ghastly",
  "book.netherman.page5.line2": "可用緋紅菌柄建造蜂巢，",
  "book.netherman.page5.line3": "能夠生產緋紅蜂蜜，",
  "book.netherman.page5.line4": "可以被馴服，",
  "book.netherman.page5.line5": "能夠指引地獄宅邸的位置。",
  "book.netherman.page5.line6": "§c§l次要生物：",
  "book.netherman.page5.line7": "§6Welcomer§f§l - 在入口歡迎玩家。",
  "book.netherman.page5.line8": "§6Trader§f§l - 提供各種交易。",
  "book.netherman.page5.line9": "§6鍍金魔像§f§l - 保護信徒，吸收物品與鮮血。",
  "book.netherman.page5.line10": "§4Gehinnom§f§l - 守衛，最好不要招惹。",
  "book.netherman.page5.line11": "§4Manipulator§f§l - 阿撒瀉勒的僕從，負責資源管理。",

  "book.netherman.page6.line1": "§c§l物品",
  "book.netherman.page6.line2": "§c重生圖騰：",
  "book.netherman.page6.line3": "受到致命傷害時會傳送至重生點。",
  "book.netherman.page6.line4": "§4操縱法杖：",
  "book.netherman.page6.line5": "可施加操縱效果，",
  "book.netherman.page6.line6": "拉動實體並召喚凋零骷髏。",
  "book.netherman.page6.line7": "§e§l感謝遊玩！",
  "book.netherman.page6.line8": "作者：§4Benj1kus",

